d level  features the ability to capture market gains up to a cap or maximum growth opportunity in one of  indices – sp  index russell ® index and msci eafe index at the end of the one year term builtin protection of a  shield rate from index loss the flexibility to choose yearly whether to continue tracking the current indexselect a new index to track or allocate the account value to a fixed account if available and an included return of premium death benefit offering additional protection of the investment shield level  is designed as a longterm accumulation vehicle and has a six year withdrawal charge schedule however consumers can withdraw up to  percent of their account value each year without a surrender penalty beginning in the second contract year after six years the consumer gains access to the full account balance without withdrawal chargefor detailed product information please see the prospectus at brighthousefinancialcomshieldlevelabout brighthouse financialbrighthouse financial is an operating segment of metlife inc met and a leading annuity and life insurance provider in the us with approximately  million insurance policies and annuity contracts inforce as of december   our mission is to help consumers achieve financial security by offering essential life insurance and annuity solutions designed to protect what they have earned and help ensure it lasts learn more at wwwbrighthousefinancialcomabout metlifemetlife inc met through its subsidiaries and affiliates metlife is one of the largest life insurance companies in the world founded in  metlife is a global provider of life insurance annuities employee benefits and asset management serving approximately  million customers metlife has operations in nearly  countries and holds leading market positions in the united states japan latin america asia europe and the middle east for more information visit wwwmetlifecomthe sp  index is a product of sp dow jones indices llc “spdji” and has been licensed for use 