 financial brand in march and reflects brighthouse financial’s mission to help people protect what they’ve earned and help ensure that it lasts metlife inc has initiated the regulatory process for the planned separation of brighthouse financial shield level  an indexlinked single premium deferred annuity with no annual fees was designed in response to distributor requests for a shield level selector product with a streamlined set of features and options providing an innovative approach to combining market participation and protection shield level  allows retirement savers to take advantage of the growth opportunities in equities markets while being protected from the first  percent of index loss wells fargo advisors will serve as initial distributors for shield level  “we are pleased to offer our clients retirement strategies such as shield level  to help them protect and grow their retirement savings” said bernie gacona senior vice president director of annuities wells fargo advisors “shield level  is one part investment and one part protection against index loss” said myles lambert chief distribution and marketing officer brighthouse financial “given consumers’ positive response to shield level selector we are excited to be working with wells fargo advisors to bring to market the newest member of our flagship annuity product family” shield level  features the ability to capture market gains up to a cap or maximum growth opportunity in one of  indices – sp  index russell ® index and msci eafe index at the end of the one year term builtin protection of a  shield rate from index loss the flexibility to choose yearly whether to continue tracking the current indexselect a new index to track or allocate the account value to a fixed account if available and an included return of premium death benefit offering additional protection of the investment shield level  is designed as a longterm accumulation vehicle and has a six year withdrawal charge schedule however consumers can withdraw up to  percent of their account value each year without a surrender penalty beginning in the second contract year after six years the consumer gains access to the full account balance without withdrawal charge for detailed product information please see the prospectus at brighthousefinancialcomshieldlevel about brighthouse financial brighthouse financial is an operating segment of metlife inc nysemet and a leading annuity and life insurance provider in the us with approximately  million insurance policies and annuity contracts inforce as of december   our mission is to help consumers achieve financial security by offering essential life insurance and annuity solutions designed to protect what they have earned and help ensure it lasts learn more at wwwbrighthousefinancialcom about metlife metlife inc nyse met through its subsidiaries and affiliates metlife is one of the largest life insurance companies in the world founded in  metlife is a global provider of life insurance annuities employee benefits and asset management serving approximately  million customers metlife has operations in nearly  countries and holds leading market positions in the united states japan latin america asia europe and the middle east for more information visit wwwmetlifecom the sp  index is a product of sp dow jones indices llc “spdji” and has been licensed for use by affiliates of brighthouse financial inc including brighthouse services llc brighthouse life insurance company and brighthouse life insurance company of ny collectively “brighthouse financial” standard  poor’s® sp® and sp ® are registered trademarks of standard  poor’s financial services llc “sp” dow jones® is a registered trademark of dow jones trademark holdings llc “dow jones” and these trademarks have been licensed for use by spdji and sublicensed for certain purposes by brighthouse financial this annuity product is not sponsored endorsed sold or promoted by spdji dow jones sp their respective affiliates and n